channel.title: UMF Miami
channel.description:
For the ones who are not able to go to Miami I would like to remind you that there is a live stream going this weekend starting in a few hours:
Link for the Live stream: http://twitch.tv/ultra Link for the Line-up: http://www.ultramusicfestival.com/lineup
Enjoy the best beats and newest tunes from the best Dj`s in the world this weekend! The festival starts at 4 pm EST.
